skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: coffee shop sounds
des: Use Alexa to transport you straight to a quaint, lively coffee shop. The audio has been chosen so as not to be too intrusive making it perfect to listen to as you work, or maybe read a book. It includes murmured conversation in the background, the sound of the occasional blender whipping up something delicious and some cutlery for people digging into their snacks.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
